WEBVTT

00:03:59.198 --> 00:04:01.326
so that millions of workers
around the world

00:04:01.350 --> 00:04:03.660
have unbelievably boring working lives.

00:04:04.057 --> 00:04:05.928
(Laughter)

00:04:06.427 --> 00:04:08.829
Let's take the example
of a call center agent.

00:04:08.853 --> 00:04:11.856
Over the last few decades,
we brag about lower operating costs

00:04:11.880 --> 00:04:14.307
because we've taken most
of the need for brainpower

00:04:14.331 --> 00:04:16.475
out of the person
and put it into the system.

00:04:16.499 --> 00:04:19.020
For most of their day,
they click on screens,

00:04:19.044 --> 00:04:20.245
they read scripts.

00:04:21.487 --> 00:04:24.140
They act more like machines than humans.

00:04:25.278 --> 00:04:27.394
And unfortunately,
over the next few years,

00:04:27.418 --> 00:04:29.277
as our technology gets more advanced,

00:04:29.301 --> 00:04:31.885
they, along with people
like clerks and bookkeepers,